Modern Family star Sofia Vergara flaunted her stunning complexion over the weekend as she showed off her birthday celebrations on social media. The actress marked her 50th birthday in style with an elegant party that included a table covered in floral arrangements and a special cake featuring a photo of her as a child. Other pictures of the actress showed her posing alongside different cakes and a number of her party guests. One of the snaps featured an age-defying Sofia posing alongside a Louis Vuitton bag-shaped cake, with the star captioning the shot: “Thank u everyone for all the bday wishes!!!” (sic)